1. Imamo velike *zalihe* hrane i vode za slučaj prirodnih katastrofa. (We have large *reserves* of food and water in case of natural disasters.)
2. Fabrika je smanjila *zalihe* sirovina zbog nestašice na tržištu. (The factory reduced its *stocks* of raw materials due to market shortages.)
3. Potrebno je obnoviti *zalihe* knjiga u biblioteci kako bi se zadovoljile potrebe članova. (It's necessary to replenish the *supplies* of books in the library to meet the members' needs.)
4. Zbog neodgovornog rukovanja, *zalihe* goriva su iscurile iz spremnika. (Due to irresponsible handling, the *stockpile* of fuel leaked out of the tank.)
5. Prodavnica je obnovila *zalihe* robe nakon novogodišnjih praznika. (The store replenished its *inventory* of goods after the New Year holidays.)
6. Ovo područje je poznato po velikim *zalihama* uglja. (This area is known for its large *reserves* of coal.)
7. Nismo uspeli da nabavimo dovoljno *zaliha* za projekat na vreme. (We didn't manage to procure enough *supplies* for the project on time.)
8. *Zalihe* su uvek važne u vojnim operacijama kako bi se osiguralo snabdevanje. (*Supplies* are always important in military operations to ensure provision.)